      <title>沙莱特称，经济正在放缓，但远未陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/economy-is-slowing-but-not-in-recession-shalett-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利财富管理首席信息官丽莎·沙莱特表示，美国经济正在放缓，但还远未陷入衰退。她正在接受《彭博收盘》采访。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-09/economy-is-slowing-but-not-in-recession-shalett-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 20:04:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
