      <title>自 2011 年以来，对冲基金对大宗商品的悲观看法最为盛行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/hedge-funds-most-bearish-on-commodities-since-at-least-2011</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心经济进一步放缓，人们对原油、金属和谷物等商品的需求产生怀疑，对大宗商品价格的悲观看法至少达到 13 年来最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/hedge-funds-most-bearish-on-commodities-since-at-least-2011</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 19:52:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
